---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — EuroVisaCalculator"
  description="EuroVisaCalculator is a client-side tool. Your travel data never leaves your device. Learn what we collect, what we don't, and how the tool works."
  canonicalUrl="https://eurovisacalculator.com/privacy"
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="page__inner">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to EuroVisaCalculator</a>

      <h1 class="page__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page__date">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">What this tool does</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          EuroVisaCalculator is a client-side web application. Your trip dates,
          traveler names, and travel history are stored in your browser only —
          in your URL and in your browser's local storage. This data never
          leaves your device to our servers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">What we collect</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          We collect anonymous usage events to understand how the tool is used
          and to improve it. These events include actions like "trip added" or
          "link copied", along with your approximate screen size and browser
          type. We do not collect your name, email address, IP address, or any
          actual travel dates.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">What we don't do</h2>
        <ul class="section__list">
          <li>We do not sell data to anyone</li>
          <li>We do not share data with third parties</li>
          <li>We do not run advertising</li>
          <li>We do not store your travel history on our servers</li>
          <li>We do not use cookies for tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">Local storage</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          Your trip data is saved in your browser's local storage so it persists
          between visits. You can clear this at any time by clearing your browser
          data, or by using the "Reset all data" option in the app. You can also
          share your data with others via the shareable URL — only people you
          share that URL with can see your trips.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">Analytics</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          We use a lightweight, self-hosted analytics setup. No third-party
          analytics platforms (such as Google Analytics) are used. The anonymous
          event data we collect is used solely to understand feature usage and
          fix bugs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">Legal disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          EuroVisaCalculator is an informational tool only. Results should not be
          relied upon as legal advice or as a guarantee of entry into the Schengen
          Area. Always verify your travel dates against official records, including
          your passport stamps. We recommend leaving a buffer of at least 2 days
          below your maximum allowance to account for unexpected travel disruptions.
          Border decisions are made at the discretion of individual member state
          authorities.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section__title">Contact</h2>
        <p class="section__body">
          Questions? Reach us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@eurovisacalculator.com" class="inline-link">
            hello@eurovisacalculator.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #F7F5F1;
    padding: 64px 24px 96px;
  }

  .page__inner {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #5a6a82;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #0C1E3C;
  }

  .page__title {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0C1E3C;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .page__date {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #8fa0b4;
    margin: 0 0 48px;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .section__title {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0C1E3C;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .section__body {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .section__list {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .section__list li {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: #0C1E3C;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .inline-link:hover {
    color: #00B96B;
  }
</style>
